'''Miradyne Limited''', also known as '''Miradyne Computer Systems''', was a small-time manufacturer of [[Starship/Legends|starship]] avionics packages that went out of business during the height of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Miradyne supplied components for the [[Z-10 Seeker-class scout ship|Z-10 Seeker]] [[Scout/Legends|scout]] ship and when the company went out of business, this made it difficult to find replacement parts for the Z-10.<ref name="Message to Spacers">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/Mesop6|text=Message to Spacers 6}}</ref>

